name: CyberFunk_BR_2077
description: After the big soy crop crash of 2068, the ‘República Federativa do Brasil’ became the ‘República Evangélica do Pantanal’. Large cities started enforcing a brutal curfew - any person roaming the streets at forbidden times is shot on sight. Arriving in your neighborhood, you realize it's past curfew time. Your mission is to make it home alive. Use WASD to move, and LShift or Space to shoot.
